Salgado Says Meeting Spain’s Deficit Goal Is Priority This Year

-- B y   E m m a   R o s s - T h o m a s
-- 
2011-10-05T07:12:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-05/salgado-says-meeting-spain-s-deficit-goal-is-priority-this-year.html
Finance Minister  Elena Salgado  said
meeting  Spain ’s budget-deficit goal is the “priority” for the
rest of this year. The slowdown in the economy isn’t only being
caused by budget cuts, she said in an interview with Onda Cero
radio today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
